claim: Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older
explanation: The image is a portion of the full prescribing information for Flublok (Influenza Vaccine). In the “INDICATIONS AND USAGE” section it states verbatim: “Flublok is approved for use in persons 18 years of age and older.” This directly confirms and supports the claim that Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older.
